## 🚀 How to Run Locally

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/Thanusha2520/product-picks.git

# 2. Open in your IDE

# 3. Import the database
mysql -u root -p < products.sql

# 4. Update DB credentials in DBConnection.java

# 5. Deploy on Apache Tomcat or run locally
```

